snippet.title: Psychology at the University of Edinburgh
snippet.description:
This channel is for videos relating to Psychology at the University of Edinburgh. It is operated by the School of Philosophy, Psychology and Language Sciences.

Find out more about Psychology at the University of Edinburgh: http://www.ed.ac.uk/ppls/psychology

Banner image is public domain. Source: http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Sobo_1909_624.png
